{"tid":1609360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肺部出血嚴重　需靠人工心肺續命　","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T14:46:18.000Z","uid":72009,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"834cfb67507b710a326ea04a7c90b0128281b009","tid":1609360,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"警方今日下午四時許在荃灣海壩街一帶清場期間，警方曾於荃灣海壩街近川龍街發射實彈，一名示威者、中五學生被警方近距離射擊，情況危殆，目前轉送伊利沙伯醫院深切治療部。消息指，男子肺主動脈無損，但有氣胸，估計由於肺部出血嚴重，需要使用人工心肺（ECMO）續命。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，子彈並沒有傷及中鎗男子的肝、脊骨、心臟，子彈在背部，但多處肋骨斷裂。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，中鎗男子在伊院成功取出彈頭，現正在該院深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇讀醫ching , 是否好危險？？"},{"pid":"e81f03f5898359cc7844df8efbb683c7d4314b5e","tid":1609360,"uid":119609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MwX28K1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwX28K1.png&h=3d12936a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed1986b234433c4216d57ed83dc730345cc6737","tid":1609360,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:23:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a835dab9098e1091d2b2083d271ec59e0309224","tid":1609360,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb9bbe8685960d61605c3f6af611be97abfecdf","tid":1609360,"uid":245767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"(不能再有手足受傷) 放棄陣地，全面遊擊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609359</a>"},{"pid":"dc0db5bc7420171dad9d571951b2217d3dae69a5","tid"